creator: Solentro
descriptionHtml:
Solentro - make your own photo book
Thousands of happy customers. Make your own photo book, a memory for life. Choose photos from your mobile phone and the photo book will be ready in minutes – it’s easy and fun! Photo books of the highest quality - the perfect gift. Your photo books are stored automatically and you can work on them whenever you like.

HOW SOLENTRO WORKS:
- Choose up to 500 images from your mobile phone
- The app will design a beautiful photo book automatically
- Add text if you like
- Change the layout if you like
- Each photo book is available from 20-200 pages

OUR PHOTO BOOKS
XL: 11x11 inches/270x270 mm, Hard cover Deluxe, 20-200 pages
This photo book meets professional standards. The inner pages are printed on high quality 170g paper. The durability and quality of this book distinguishes it from others, a perfect choice for a professional photo book.

SOLENTRO FEATURES
- Automatic design simplifies the creation of your photo book
- Drag and drop to change the photo placement in no time
- Work from your phone in both vertical and landscape mode
- Stylish design
- Worldwide shipping
- Your photo books and images are saved and stored automatically so you can work on your photo book whenever you like!

HERE’S WHAT PEOPLE THINK ABOUT SOLENTRO:
"Easy, quick, perfect. Completed a 62-page book at reasonable cost and it made a fantastic gift!"

"Super easy to use for a fair price. End result turned out really well as well as quick delivery. Strongly recommend."

"The finished product arrived on time and we are very pleased with the quality. It is now amongst our most treasured possessions."

"Excellent service, great product, would definitely use Solentro again"

"Great quality and very quick production. We love it and we're sure the recipient will too. Highly recommended!"

"The book looked perfect just the way i imagined!"

"Solentro made making a family memory book fun and affordable!"

"This is my 2nd Solentro book and they really are excellent - high quality and, now I am on my 2nd one, easy to use. No hesitation in recommending these photo books."

"Simple process, very high quality book and speedy delivery - thank you!”

Read more great reviews here: https://www.trustpilot.com/review/solentro.co.uk

Questions? Let us know at info@solentro.com
